Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:17.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그럼 나도 같이 아플래!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아 맞다! 얼마 전에 감기 걸렸을 때\N아빠랑 같이 병원갔다?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,알고 있어, 아빠한테 들었단다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,장하네, 약도 잘 먹을 수 있게 됐다면서?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,미안해....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,감기 걸렸을 때 옆에 있어주지 못 해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마, 봐봐!\N 포켓몬!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.94,Default,Default,0,0,0,,저건 달콤아라는 포켓몬이야
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,귀여워어!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,잡아 볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,할 수 있어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,운이 좋다면... \N될지도!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,몬스터볼!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:52.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.19,Default,Default,0,0,0,,제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,잡은 거야!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,오늘 우리들....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,운이 좋아!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.94,Default,Default,0,0,0,,잘 부탁해, 달콤아!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,귀여워어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,나의....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,여동생!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,여동생인가!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.44,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그리고 얼마 안 지나...\N엄마는 다시 입원해서....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,병문안을 갈 때마다 \N미안하다는 말이 점점 많아져선...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,언제나 사과만 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,사과만 하는 엄마...\N나는 싫어..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아프셔서 어쩔 수 없던 것도...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:43.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이제야... \N지금은 알 수 있어, 엄마의 마음...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오 쨩....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하지만 그 때엔...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:50.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,"미안해, 미안해" 라고만 하는 엄마,\N나는 싫단말야!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,싫단 말야!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그게 엄마와의 마지막 대화가 돼 버렸어....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,만나고 싶지 않아....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:11.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그런 말을 해버려선....\N만날 수 없어...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이렇게 많은 인원이 \N우리 집에 머무는 건 오랜만이구나
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,두근두근거리는 구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,신세 지겠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,미안, 달코퀸.\N걱정 끼쳤지?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,모두들 미안!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,뭘, 신경쓰지 말거라
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그래 그래!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,맞아요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,있지, 하푸우네 집에선 뭐하고 놀아?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그 전에 포니 무의 씨앗 심는 걸 도와줘야 한다고!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그랬습니다....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,커다란 포니 무가 자랄 수 있도록!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,자, 다음은...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.23,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이런 걸 혼자서 해왔다니...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,굉장해, 해푸우!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하나, 둘!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,실버디, 에어슬래시!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,루가루암, 스톤에지!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.73,Default,Default,0,0,0,,혹시.... 카푸느지느의 안개인가!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,모두 있는가!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,대답하는 게야!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하푸우, 어디야?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,나는 여기야!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,움직이지 마! \N지금 거기로 갈게!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.73,Default,Default,0,0,0,,방금 전까진 좋았던 날씨가....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어제의 안개와 똑같아!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,나머지는?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:17.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오! 릴리에! 지우! \N내 목소리가 들리는가, 대답하게!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,키아웨! 마마네!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어이!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:33.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,모두들! 어디 있는 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,수련!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:44.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이상하네요...\N하푸우네 밭이 이렇게 넓었었나....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,다행이다...\N저, 안개 속에서 헤매어 버리는 줄....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,릴리에?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,오라버니!? \N어째서 여기에...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,너야말로... \N어째서 이런 숲에...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:10:00.02,Default,Default,0,0,0,,숲...?\N여긴 하푸우네 밭일텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:03.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,저, 모두와 하푸우네 집에 있었어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:03.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,뭐야?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느의 안개?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오 쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,지우야!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,릴리에, 어디야?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느의 안개에 갇혀 버린 게다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느의 안개 속은...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:23.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이 세상과 저 세상이 뒤섞이는 신비한 세계.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오와 아이들은 가까이 있는 것처럼 보이지만,\N사실은 저 멀리 떨어져 있을지도 몰라.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,지금은 없는, 누군가와 만나기 위해!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,릴리에가 말했었지, 아버지와 만나고 싶다고!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오 쨩도 분명 마오 엄마에게!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그럼 지우는?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,지우도 이 안개 속에서 \N만나고 싶은 누군가가 있는 건가?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,기다려, 냐오히트!\N어디가는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,뭐 하는 거야...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.22,Default,Default,0,0,0,,포켓몬 GET이다!\N자막: 포켓몬스터 애니 마이너 갤러리
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(500,0)\fs40\blur3\pos(134.667,478)}이름: 카푸느지느\N{\fs40}타입: 물/페어리
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,바랜드?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,진짜 바랜드다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,믿겨지질 않아 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,오랜만이구나, 바랜드!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,뭐 어때,\N만나고 싶었던 바랜드와 만났으니!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그치, 냐오히트?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.02,Default,Default,0,0,0,,불꽃엄니 로토!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이번엔 니트로차지다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,다음은 불꽃세례 로토!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이 녀석, 할 수 있는 기술 전부 \N바랜드에게 보이고 싶은 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,굉장해!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:24.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,바랜드 펀치로 불꽃세례가 불대문자가 됐다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,바랜드의 특훈이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:37.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이 안개 속 어딘가에 있는 거야? \N아버지!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:40.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아버님, 릴리에예요!\N만나게 된다면 기쁠 거예요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아버지!\N있다면 모습을 보여 줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아버지!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어쩌지... \N길을 잃어 버렸어...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.48,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:10.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.02,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,많이 컸구나, 마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,달콤아도 훌륭하게 진화하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:38.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,죄송해요, 엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:45.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,싫다고 말해서...\N죄송해요!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,괜찮단다, 마오...\N괜찮아...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그래도... 그래도.....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.56,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그건 말야, 엄마가 잘못한 거야.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,내 실수였어.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그렇지 않아요...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,넌 전혀 잘못하지 않았단다.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,들으렴, 마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:12.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마는 말야, '미안해'가 아니라 \N이렇게 말해야 했던 거였어.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,'고마워' 라고!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워, 마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마의 아이로 태어나 줘서.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:29.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워, 엄마나 아빠, 오빠에게...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,커다란 행복을 안겨 주어서!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워, 달콤아를 소중히 키워 주어서!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:46.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워, 아이나식당을 훌륭히 지켜 주어서!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:52.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워, 이렇게 예쁘고\N정직한 아이로 자라 주어서!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:53.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:54.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.70,Default,Default,0,0,0,,저, 다시 말할게요.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그러니 좀 전의 '미안해'는 잊어 주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마... 고마워요..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,언제나 상냥하고 따뜻한 엄마로 계셔 주셔서!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:23.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워요!\N매일 맛있는 밥을 만들어 주셔서!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:29.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워요..\N엄마와 함께했던 산책 무척 즐거웠어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:37.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워요,\N제가 외로워지지 않도록, 달콤아를 잡아 주셔서..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.22,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:44.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워요,\N절 낳아 주셔서!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,수련, 키아웨, 마마네!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,여기서 모두가 돌아오는 걸 기다리는 게다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.02,Default,Default,0,0,0,,만마드!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,조금 갈라졌다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.84,Default,Default,0,0,0,,힘내, 냐오히트!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,냐오히트의 불꽃세례가,\N불대문자로 진화했다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.61,Default,Default,0,0,0,,해냈어, 냐오히트!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,만마드, 여기서 기다리거라
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.05,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느여!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,릴리에와 마오, 지우를 돌려 보내 주었음 하네!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:00.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,모두가 이쪽 세계로 돌아올 수 없게 되기 전에!\N부탁하네!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,느긋하게 춤 출 때가 아니란 말이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,혹시나, 모두를 되돌려주지 않을 작정이라면...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,힘으로라도 돌려 받겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,가자, 골루그!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,러스터캐논!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이건?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하푸우.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,할아버지!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:44.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하푸우, 카푸느지느가 널\N포니 섬의 섬의 여왕으로 인정했다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,정말인가!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:50.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,네가 친구들을 구하기 위해 쏜 러스터캐논....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:55.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그것이야말로 카푸느지느의 마음을 움직인 게야.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,축하한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.22,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그럼... 카푸느지느!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,안개가...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,언제나, 곁에 있으니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:37.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,눈에는 보이지 않지만, 마음은 마오나 아빠, 오빠와\N틀림없이 이어져 있으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.76,Default,Default,0,0,0,,바랜드!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,안개가 사라져간다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:36.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.39,Default,Default,0,0,0,,여긴...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,릴리에! 글라디오!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,지우!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.52,Default,Default,0,0,0,,저기!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,무사했구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,걱정했다구!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.27,Default,Default,0,0,0,,모두~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.97,Default,Default,0,0,0,,마오 쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:55.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,다행이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그건 환상의 포켓몬, 쉐이미다 로토!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,쉐이미?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.35,Default,Default,0,0,0,,쉐이미, 감사 포켓몬.\N풀 타입.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.77,Default,Default,0,0,0,,몸을 웅크리면, 꽃 같이 보인다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그라데시아 꽃이 필 무렵,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:12.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,감사의 마음을 전하기 위해 모습을 바꿔 날아 오른다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.64,Default,Default,0,0,0,,함께 있어 줄래?\N네가 언딘가로 날아 오를 때까지!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,고마워!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,귀여워, 쉐이미!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:25.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,수련... \N만났어...엄마와!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,우리는, 바랜드와 만났어!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,저희들은....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어째서 아버지는 모습을 나타내지 않은 거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:40.14,Default,Default,0,0,0,,살아 있으니까, 이지 않은가?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:49.02,Default,Default,0,0,0,,너희들이 강하게 바랬음에도 \N모습을 드러내지 않은 건,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,아버지는 살아있는 게다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이 넓고 넓은 세계 어딘가에서 말이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.60,Default,Default,0,0,0,,이 넓고 넓은 세계....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.89,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어딘가에....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.10,Default,Default,0,0,0,,어머니에게 전해야 해!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.18,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그래요!\N조금이라도 빠르게!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:04.93,Default,Default,0,0,0,,실버디!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,글라디오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:12.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,다음에 포니 섬에 찾아오면,\N큰 시련을 받게 해 주마!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그건 설마...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:19.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느가 나를 섬의 여왕으로서 인정한 게야.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.26,Default,Default,0,0,0,,섬의 여왕, 폭탄! (爆誕)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,축하해, 하푸우!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.06,Default,Default,0,0,0,,축하해요!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.68,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그럼 그럼, 지금부터 큰 시련을 받게 해 주세요, \N섬의 여왕님!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,하여간, 성급한 녀석이구나. \N지우는.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,큰 시련은 말이다, \N내가 섬의 여왕이 되는 의식이 끝나고 나서다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.72,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그럼 의식이 끝나면!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.81,Default,Default,0,0,0,,받아 들이마!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,카푸느지느의 안개 속에서 어머니와 만난 마오.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:47.31,Default,Default,0,0,0,,스승, 바랜드와 만난 냐오히트.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:52.47,Default,Default,0,0,0,,그들은 귀중한 경험을 가슴 속에, \N다시 한 번한 걸음 앞으로 나아갔다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:57.85,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,690)}그리고 지우는, 포니 섬의 큰 시련이 기다리고 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:08.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,310)\fsp-1}오늘아침 비에 젖은 논두렁 길은 햇빛을 뒤집어 쓰고
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:08.43,Default,Default,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,310)\fsp-1}오늘아침 비에 젖은 논두렁 길은 햇빛을 뒤집어 쓰고
